==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Zygophyte
<hw>Zy"go*phyte</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Gr.
<grk>zygo`n</grk> a yoke + <grk>fyto`n</grk> a plant.]</ety>
<fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>Any plant of a proposed class or grand division
(<class>Zygophytes</class>, <class>Zygophyta</class>, or
<class>Zygosporeae</class>), in which reproduction consists in the union
of two similar cells. Cf. <er>Oophyte</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source> + <source>CM</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Zygoptera</ent>⟦br⟧
